description: Try our easy to follow Smashed Potato & Corn Frittata recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Smashed Potato & Corn Frittata Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 cup leftover roast potatoes, roughly chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 190Â°C. Grease a 4-cup baking dish.
Place potato in base of dish and top with spinach, corn, tomato and onion. Whisk eggs and cream together in a jug and season. Pour mixture over potato. Scatter over cheeses.
Bake for 30-35 minutes or until golden and just firm to touch. Cut into wedges and serve warm or at room temperature with a salad.
